        "description": "Smaller for fine surface preparation on pine, larger for broad industrial areas; 200 μm optimal for uniform energy distribution without pinpoint damage. Source: Equipment specifications from manufacturers like Coherent and Trumpf lasers for cleaning heads (typical 150-300 μm for organic substrates)."
